OL,5,G1700 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,6,G     Speeders
OL,7,     FMultiple units race to catch a
OL,8,     Fgroup of potential car thieves.
OL,9,     FAnd police respond to a 999 call
OL,10,     Fabout a motorbike driving the
OL,11,     Fwrong way into oncoming traffic.
OL,12,G1800 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FCases include a raid on a
OL,14,     Fsuspected drug user whose door
OL,15,     Fwon't budge, a chase after a
OL,16,     Fsouped-up hot hatch and a
OL,17,     Flate-night reveller in Nantwich
OL,18,     Ftown centre.
