OL,5,G2100 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FDoors get smashed in dawn raids on
OL,7,     Fdrug dealers, shots are fired in a
OL,8,     Fsuburban siege, and bad guys are
OL,9,     Fchased at more than 100mph.
OL,10,G2200 Cops
OL,11,     FA suspect who fled on an
OL,12,     Funlicenced dirt bike begs to go
OL,13,     Fhome. A man with a warrant for
OL,14,     Fdomestic battery is caught with
OL,15,     Ffentanyl. A citizen calls 911 when
OL,16,     Fshe observes a dispute.
OL,17,G2230 Cops
OL,18,     FStop Sticks are used to end the
OL,19,     Fpursuit of a man that deputies
OL,20,     Fhave previously arrested. Sisters
OL,21,     Fargue over access to their elderly
OL,22,     Fmother.
